criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients aged 18-60 with mandibular condylar fractures were treated in Oral and
             maxillofacial surgery department, West China hospital of stomatology, China from
             January 2014 to January 2016.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients refused to participate in the clinical trial;

          -  condylar fracture dislocation was not obvious, conservative treatment can be used;

          -  mandibular condylar comminuted fracture;

          -  mandibular condyle need to be reconstructed.
